# Lint and Type-Check After Changes

After every code change, run the linter and type-check. Any errors must be resolved.

## Workflow

1. **Run lint:** `npm run lint`
2. **Run type-check:** `npm run type-check`
3. **If errors are found:** Fix them before considering the change complete. Do not leave lint or type errors unfixed.

## Commands

| Command | Purpose |
|---------|---------|
| `npm run lint` | ESLint – reports style and logic issues |
| `npm run type-check` | TypeScript `tsc --noEmit` – reports type errors |

Do not submit or finalize changes until both pass.
